title: The Supreme Way
description: The Supreme Way ManhuaThis is a world where all people have the hope of becoming gods. Taking the path of the Thunder God, one can become a Thunder God. After taking the path of Mountain God, one can become a Mountain God. After becoming a god, one can open up a divine kingdom. The crossover Lai Cang had no money and no talent to take the God path, but in an accident, he became the first in history to open up God kingdom before becoming a God! The Supreme Godly Way Wú Shàng Shén Tú 无上神途 Divine Path to Supremacy
